				<a href="//sinosphere.blogs.nytimes.com/2015/11/19/china-hostage-islamic-state-fan-jinghui/"><img src="https://static01.nyt.com/images/2015/11/19/world/19sino-hostage/19sino-hostage-thumbStandard.jpg" width="50" height="50" /></a>
			</div>
						<h5><a href="//sinosphere.blogs.nytimes.com/2015/11/19/china-hostage-islamic-state-fan-jinghui/" title="Read: Chinese Debate Proper Response to Hostage&rsquo;s Killing">Chinese Debate Proper Response to Hostage&rsquo;s Killing</a>
			<span class="postMetaHeaderCommentCount commentCount hidden">
					<i class="icon"></i>
					<a class="commentCountLink commentCountNumberOnly commentCountNoPrompt" href="//sinosphere.blogs.nytimes.com/2015/11/19/china-hostage-islamic-state-fan-jinghui/"></a>
				</span>			</h5>
			<p class="summary">
